author: Darrell Etherington
title: Rocket Lab postpones next mission due to coronavirus pandemic
description: Rocket Lab is the latest new space company to feel the impact of the global coronavirus pandemic: The small satellite launcher announced on Tuesday that it would be suspending its next launch, a mission called ‘Don’t Stop Me Now’ that was set to take-off from…
